UK Gunworks is a family-run business, established in 2009 to fill a gap in the rifle market. Our work is always high quality, punctual and affordable.

Chris Blackburn, founder of UK Gunworks, originally began keepering in Scotland on a mixed sporting estate before re-training in engineering. This led to him work for Pro-Drive, the Subaru World Rally Team. The combination of Chris’s keepering experience and the precision skills acquired in gear-box engineering has given him an excellent foundation to build and repair rifles.

ONLINE SHOP

Please visit our online shop to browse our selection of clothing, shooting accessories and fishing equipment. >

T3 Trigger springs back in stock

As well as the T3 springs we have another batch of action screws due in very soon along with our updated bolt knobs and handles.
